服務廣告協議.pinyin: fú wù guǎng gào xié yì

服務臺.definition: service desk; information desk; reception desk

服帖.definition: docile; obedient; appropriate; fitting; at ease; comfortable

服役.definition: to serve in the army; in active service

服從.definition: to obey (an order); to comply; to defer

服法.definition: to submit to the law; to obey the law; administration method (of medicine)

服滿.definition: to have completed the mourning period (traditional); to have served one's time

服罪.definition: to admit to a crime; to plead guilty

服老.definition: to admit to one's advancing years; to acquiesce to old age

服貿.definition: Cross-Strait Service Trade Agreement; abbr. for 兩岸服務貿易協議|两岸服务贸易协议[Liang3 an4 Fu2 wu4 Mao4 yi4 Xie2 yi4]
